text.plain_text: 1. What is Bankless DAO?

text.content: Bankless DAO is a decentralized community focused on driving adoption and awareness of bankless money systems like Ethereum, Bitcoin and DeFi.

text.content: 8. What is the Genesis Proposal?

text.plain_text: 8. What is the Genesis Proposal?

text.content: The Genesis Proposal has closed for voting but is essential reading for DAO contributors, as it lays the foundation for key infrastructure of the Bankless DAO

text.plain_text: The Genesis Proposal has closed for voting but is essential reading for DAO contributors, as it lays the foundation for key infrastructure of the Bankless DAO

text.content: https://snapshot.org/#/banklessvault.eth/proposal/QmdoixPMMT76vSt6ewkE87JZJywS1piYsGC3nJJpcrPXKS

text.plain_text: https://snapshot.org/#/banklessvault.eth/proposal/QmdoixPMMT76vSt6ewkE87JZJywS1piYsGC3nJJpcrPXKS

text.content: The Genesis Proposal is the first proposal by Bankless LLC to grant a portion of the community treasury to the company in order to act as core participants in the DAO. Since BANK was a fair launch, Bankless LLC did not receive any BANK. It’s up to the community to choose its path.

text.content: 9. I donated to Bankless through Gitcoin but didn’t get BANK?

text.plain_text: 9. I donated to Bankless through Gitcoin but didn’t get BANK?

text.content: If you donated more than $0.95 to Bankless through Gitcoin, but your address shows ‘0 BANK’ when you try and claim https://www.bankless.community/claim, please send a DM to our community manager @Above Average Joe with the details of your donation.

text.content: 10. I tried joining but didn’t receive a response from the Collab.Land bot?

text.plain_text: 10. I tried joining but didn’t receive a response from the Collab.Land bot?

text.content: Check that your Discord settings allow you to receive direct messages and make sure that the wallet you are connecting with has 35,000 BANK. Type !join in #join and try again.
